            "title": "將軍澳蔚藍灣畔2房戶708萬成交   持貨4年蝕142萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15021038&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">利嘉閣地產將軍澳蔚藍灣畔二行促成將軍澳蔚藍灣畔6座中層A室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約506方呎，屬2房間隔，遠望山景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該行稱，新買家為區內換樓客，業主原叫價760萬元，議價至708萬元成交，折合實用面積呎價約13,992元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據悉，原業主於2021年以約850萬元買入單位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該屋苑現有約79個單位放盤，最低入場費由約680萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15021038-%e5%b0%87%e8%bb%8d%e6%be%b3%e8%94%9a%e8%97%8d%e7%81%a3%e7%95%942%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6708%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a84%e5%b9%b4%e8%9d%95142%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-19 18:11:14",
            "source": "bastillepost",
